{"type": "article", "id": 20623, "title": "钻石灯泡", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-13T07:30:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606141929UTwWejfyghMzKRG3.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是 Nanoleaf 团队最近推出的 Bloom 灯，他们在电路板上描出了有设计感的花纹，但外形和功能与之前的是类似的。这盏灯是用 11 块电路板拼成的，像钻石，每一块电路板都有 3 个 LED 灯泡，一共有 33 个。它有环保节电的优势，也可以调整光线的强弱，在晚上用作一盏夜灯。售价 48.99 美元，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/nanoleaf-bloom-moomin-edition/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150512PrSj9ysT7kqnb2L8.jpg\" width=\"924\" height=\"744\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80519481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150514AoPKx9USvBDdI7t5.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"940\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150515Rl6taWpTy1rGJ8e7.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"599\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.55462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150515XNA19vQLHByinSw6.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"609\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}